4.4 Planned On‚ÄëChain Transition on Cosmos

Our long‚Äëterm vision is to migrate all governance functions on‚Äëchain using a Cosmos network DApp:
	‚Ä¢	On‚ÄëChain Voting: Smart contracts will capture proposals, votes, and rewards with complete transparency.
	‚Ä¢	Integrated Dashboard: A unified interface will offer real‚Äëtime monitoring and an intuitive experience bridging web2 and web3.
	‚Ä¢	NFT Management: All Soulbound NFTs will retain their non-transferable property, ensuring permanent identity and accountability.

