5. Governance Methodology

5.1 Daily Dragon Dreaming Cycle

Our governance process is structured around a daily cycle inspired by Dragon Dreaming, consisting of four phases:
	1.	Dream Phase (00:00‚Äì03:00 UTC):
	‚Ä¢	Purpose: Submission of visionary proposals.
	‚Ä¢	Process: Members submit ideas and proposals that align with collective aspirations.
	2.	Plan Phase (03:00‚Äì07:30 UTC):
	‚Ä¢	Purpose: Refinement and planning.
	‚Ä¢	Process: Proposals are discussed and refined. If co‚Äëcreation is needed, negotiations occur regarding the redistribution of voting power (e.g., splitting the Creator NFT weight).
	3.	Realize Phase (07:30‚Äì18:00 UTC):
	‚Ä¢	Purpose: Execution and validation.
	‚Ä¢	Process: Members execute tasks and validate progress. Voting occurs to either accept the results or suggest improvements.
	4.	Celebrate Phase (18:00‚Äì22:00 UTC):
	‚Ä¢	Purpose: Recognition and reward.
	‚Ä¢	Process: Proposals that meet the quality criteria are awarded medals (Bronze, Silver, Gold, Diamond). Final vote weights are calculated, and any applicable multipliers (e.g., from Red Pill NFTs) are applied during the last 2 hours of the cycle.

5.2 Emoji Voting and Moderation

5.2.1 Voting Emojis
	‚Ä¢	Initial Vote on Proposal:
Members react with one of the following:
	‚Ä¢	Green Check (‚úÖ): Vote to accept the proposal.
	‚Ä¢	Gray X (‚ùé): Vote to request enhancements.
	‚Ä¢	Red X (‚ùå): Vote to reject, triggering the moderation process.
	‚Ä¢	Medal Vote Window (Post‚ÄëAcceptance):
Upon receiving sufficient ‚ÄúAccept‚Äù votes, a separate voting window opens where members assign a medal:
	‚Ä¢	Bronze Medal: Basic acceptance.
	‚Ä¢	Silver Medal: Moderate endorsement.
	‚Ä¢	Gold Medal: High-quality contribution.
	‚Ä¢	Diamond Medal (üíé): Initiates co‚Äëcreation negotiations (enabling dynamic redistribution of Creator NFT power).

5.2.2 Moderation Flags

When a proposal or interaction is flagged (using Red X), it enters a moderation window where Truth ID NFT holders can assign:
	‚Ä¢	Yellow Flag (üü®): First warning (12‚Äëhour standby).
	‚Ä¢	Orange Flag (üüß): Second warning (24‚Äëhour standby).
	‚Ä¢	Red Flag (üü•): Third warning (7‚Äëday standby).
	‚Ä¢	Black Flag (‚¨õ): Final warning (28‚Äëday standby and burn of the Truth ID NFT, with a mandatory re‚Äëcertification process).

