6. Economic Model & Tokenomics

6.1 Assets and Their Functions

Asset	Purpose	Control Mechanism
Truth ID NFT	Unique identity and access to governance.	Issued after completion of the educational module; non-transferable.
Creator NFT	Recognizes significant contributions; holds 51% initial voting power.	Can be split via co‚Äëcreation negotiations based on predetermined ratios.
Collaborator NFT	Acknowledges daily contributions; voting weight varies (1‚Äì7).	Weight determined based on quality of contribution; contributes to credibility ranking.
Red Pill NFT	Weekly vote multiplier based on participation and alignment.	Calculated as: \text{Multiplier} = (\% \text{Participation} \times \% \text{Alignment} \times 7); limited to 3 per wallet, oldest burned every 28 days.

6.2 Revenue Streams
	‚Ä¢	Certification Fees: Modest fees for Truth ID exams to ensure low barriers for entry.
	‚Ä¢	Dreamverse Licensing: A nominal fee (e.g., 1% on DAOs using the protocol) reinvested in community growth.
	‚Ä¢	Transaction Efficiency: Utilizing Cosmos for low-fee, multichain transactions.

