8. Security & Accountability

8.1 Anti-Rug Pull Measures
	‚Ä¢	Multisig Escrow: Funds are held in multisig wallets, requiring collective approval before release.
	‚Ä¢	Developer Verification: Only verified developers (Truth ID NFT holders) can propose changes, ensuring accountability.

8.2 Moderation and Flag System
	‚Ä¢	Tiered Warning System: A structured moderation process with escalating flags (Yellow, Orange, Red, Black) ensures community rules are upheld.
	‚Ä¢	Community-Based Resolution: All moderation actions are determined by consensus among Truth ID holders, reinforcing decentralization.

